ru.nordavind.ecgdonglelib.scan

Class DongleDataChunk

  • java.lang.Object
    • ru.nordavind.ecgdonglelib.scan.DongleDataChunk
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IRecycleable

    public class DongleDataChunk
extends java.lang.Object
implements IRecycleable
    Data chunk; Samples are provided in DongleDataChunk objects. Each DongleDataChunk contains samples for some period of time for all channels. Usually, DongleDataChunk contains 100 samples for each lead, but this amount might be changed. ECG Dongle has some hardware leads. Some leads might be calculated. For example, basic ECG Dongle has II and III hardware leads, and I, aVR, aVL, aVF leads are calculated. DongleDataChunk is able to return data samples getRawData() and calculated values in millivolts getCalculatedData(Lead, float[]). You should not change values returned by getRawData()
